              },
              "free_text": [
                " THIS REACTION WAS",
                " CHOSEN AS THE PRIMARY MONITOR SINCE THE THRESHOLD",
                " ENERGY IS SIMILAR. THE VALUE FOR THE FISSION SPECTRUM",
                " AVERAGE CROSS SECTION WAS TAKEN AS 0.21 MB.",
                " OTHER MONITORS WERE NI-58(N,2N), AL-27(N,A)NA-24",
                " AND NI-58(N,P) WITH ASSUMED VALUES FOR THE FISSION",
                " AVERAGE CROSS SECTIONS OF 0.004, 0.60 AND 102 MB",
                " RESPECTIVELY."
